data.description: Impressive Colonial style home centrally located in the City of Kenyon on a quiet street full of wonder & charm! The home is an easy stroll or bike ride to the public swimming pool. A newer storage shed is tucked in the back of the fenced in yard for extra storage. French doors off of the formal dining room will make your heart sing. This sprawling property has plenty of room for different activities whether it be playing board games, a gaming area or quiet spot to read a book or enjoy a cup of coffee. Newer Jeld Wen windows top off this fantastic home! You won't be disappointed to experience the peacefulness of small town living!
